         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="ONB_LitArchiv_00000005"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb168815" type="place">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Georg Engländer</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb59" type="place">Wien IX</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1270" type="place">Nußdorferstr <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>4</unclear></del> 10.</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="ONB_LitArchiv_00000006"/><date>20. 4. 913</date></dateline><salute>Sehr geehrter Herr,</salute></opener><p>in Angelegenheit von <rs ref="#pmb2147" type="person">Pet.</rs> den ich heute<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>prach
               (auch <hi rend="latintype">Primar</hi> Dr. <rs ref="#pmb23360" type="person">R.</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>prach ich) möchte ich gern mit Ihnen reden. We<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich Sie morgen <date>Montag</date> um
                  <time>1 Uhr</time> oder um <time>½ 7–7</time> Abend erwarten darf, bedarf es
               keiner Antwort.</p><closer>Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr ergebner <signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
